5.1 Just Adult Fishes

## [1] "This analysis includes only 5-m depth."

Fish data were log transformed for the analysis prior to calculating the dissimilartiy matrix.

Fish included were OPEL, HEXA, SECA, SCMA, SENE, SEME, EMBI, GOBI

Years included were 2016, 2017, 2018, 2019, 2021

5.2 Just Sebastes YOY

YOY data were log transformed for the analysis prior to calculating the dissimilartiy matrix.

YOY included were SECAyoy, SEPIyoy, SEMYyoy, SEBYTyoy, RYOY

Years included were 2016, 2017, 2018, 2019, 2021
